'''The Lord of the Rings MUSH II''' is a [[wikipedia:MUSH|MUSH]] created by [[Christopher Anderson]]. 

The game takes place in the [[Fourth Age]], during [[Aragorn]]'s Kingship. He sends a group of explorers - the players - to [[Rhûn|the east]] to search for the [[Blue Wizards]]. Programming began in [[1999]], but it has not been released yet. If it ever will is uncertain.
